        <qualifiedname>PanelBridge::setup</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Initialise STM32 board services, UART2, <ref refid="namespaceCANProtocol" kindref="compound">CANProtocol</ref>, and <ref refid="namespacePanelBridge" kindref="compound">PanelBridge</ref> internals. </para>
